      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your body is not self-regulating; it is a chaotic system that reacts unpredictably to diet, illness, and even minor stressors, making a \"safe trial\" of 3mg a recipe for catastrophic bleeding or clotting.\nThe danger isn't just in the drop itself, but in the invisible gap where your INR could swing wildly before you even feel sick, leaving you with no warning signs.\nThere is no logical way to adjust warfarin safely without a blood test, so please keep taking your full 5mg until you can see a doctor, even if it feels like a waste.",
